race.comment: The feature of the day now and TALKANCO (1) looks the one to beat after finishing just 0.2L away in the main lead-up last start. She's carried more weight than her rivals throughout the campaign thus far and now meets them all at level weights. She's drawn ideally and with things swinging her way today, she's the one to beat. OURGIRLCANRUN (10) backed up her impressive Maiden win with a strong performance in the Burgess Queen when setting the tempo. Blinkers come off now as she rises to the mile, but she'll give them something to chase. MOONWALK (8) ticks a few boxes today and could be an improver. PURE EXCESS (9) wasn't beaten far in the Burgess Queen as a $26 chance and has to be included.
